              Late December 2025
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-[#0D1B2A] mb-2">
              Toolzya today
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 pl-20 md:order-2">
            <div
              class="p-6 rounded-2xl
         bg-gradient-to-br from-[#e6f1f2] to-white
         border border-[#0d3d42]/30
         shadow-lg
         transition-all duration-300 ease-out
         hover:shadow-xl
         hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#415A77] leading-relaxed">
                Toolzya launched with a growing collection of AI-powered
                generators, built to be fast, accessible, and friction-free.
              </p>
